HEADWORD: Pernot furnace
<hw>Per"not fur"nace</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[So called from
<person>Charles <etsep>Pernot</etsep></person>, its inventor.]</ety>
<def>A reverberatory furnace with a circular revolving hearth, -- used
in making steel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

